FBIS4-10809 "drlat075_c_94006" FBIS-LAT-94-075 Daily Report 14 Apr 1994 MEXICO Electoral Institute Approves Zedillo Registration Electoral Institute Approves Zedillo Registration PA1604001694 Mexico City Radio ACIR Network in Spanish 0000 GMT 14 Apr 94 PA1604001694 Mexico City Radio ACIR Network Spanish BFN [From the "ACIR Radio News" newscast] [Text] Today the General Council of the Federal Electoral Institute approved without reservations Ernesto Zedillo Ponce de Leon's registration as the PRI [Institutional Revolutionary Party] presidential candidate. Zedillo, among other activities, met very early today with Mexico City newspaper vendors on the streets of Bucareli. This afternoon he also met with PRI women.
